---
// Hero.astro - 메인 페이지 히어로 섹션 컴포넌트
---

<section
  class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 py-8 md:py-12 min-h-[40vh] flex items-center"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap gap-8 items-center">
    <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text"
      >
        통통 스터디 그룹
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-medium mb-6">IT 지식 공유 플랫폼</p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
        IT, AI, Software 개발에 관한 지식을 공유하는 웹 플랫폼입니다.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="/blog"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >Blog</a
        >
        <a
          href="/wiki"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >Wiki</a
        >
        <a
          href="/apps"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >Demo Apps</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex justify-center items-center">
      <img
        src="/hero-image.svg"
        alt="TTSG 프로젝트 일러스트"
        class="max-w-full h-auto animate-float shadow-2xl rounded-xl"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
